commit b32653a35c754a752001ddd281cf65c63b54752d
Author: Steven <stevenh1607@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu Jun 18 21:03:06 2026 +1000

    design: EE brand uplift — programme header, CART P-cards, integrity stat-cards, assembly card grid
    
    - ContributionSplitTab: replace white programme header with navy #002266 card (PROGRAMME eyebrow, white name, #93B0DA mono meta, commercial total metric, 14px EE/customer split bar with legend, RIT-D amber note, report/delete toolbar in dark footer strip)
    - CART: remove P80 card; grid-cols-5 → grid-cols-4 (P10/P50/P90/Deterministic only per spec)
    - CART histogram: replace plain <text> P-marker labels with filled label chips (rounded rect + white text) at top of each dashed line
    - WBSIntegrityPanel: add 3 stat-cards after toolbar (Checks Passing n/6 green, Items to Review amber, Last Run time)
    - SourcePricingEditor Assembly: early-return 2-col card grid from matAssemblies data (mono code chip, Approved pill, name, section·n items, total_cost value)
    - FinancialScreen: header card + table/PA/SVG colours updated to var(--primary-900) / #002266 (previously hardcoded #1e3a5f)
    - ContributionSplitTab colour constants: EE_BLUE → #1F478A, CUST_ORG → #FF5300 (EE brand tokens)
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>

